  @ImplementedBy-pallavi.singh
  Scenario Outline: ACAUTOCAS-8974:  CERSAI page should get default data for collateral Property at credit approval of "<ProductType>" application at "<ApplicationStage>" stage
    And user opens an "<ProductType>" application for "<ApplicantType>" applicant at "<ApplicationStage>" for "<Category>" with "<key>" from application grid
    And user opens Collateral Page on "<ApplicationStage>" without adding New Collateral
    And user reads data from the excel file "<CollateralWB>" under sheet "<Collateral_cersaiDetails>" and row <Collateral_cersaiDetails_rowNum>
    And user adds the collateral of "<CollateralSubType>" subtype
    And user modifies the collateral of "<CollateralSubType>"
    And user reads data from the excel file "<CollateralWB>" under sheet "<Collateral_cersaiDetails>" and row <Collateral_cersaiDetails_rowNum1>
    When user enters all the fields of address details of collateral subtype
    And user enters all the information in Property and Registration Details section
    And user checks the duplicates on collateral dedupe check
    And user saves the collateral data
    And user modifies the collateral of "<CollateralSubType>"
    And user navigates to the CERSAI page
    Then user should be able to see default data in section Cersai Data
